student_attainment_description: Student Attainment measures how well the school performed on standardized tests at a single point in time. student_attainment_description: Student Attainment measures how well the school performed on standardized tests at a single point in time. student_growth_description: Student Growth measures the change in standardized test scores between two points in time. student_growth_description: Student Growth measures the change in standardized test scores between two points in time. This growth is compared to the average national growth for schools that started in the same place. A 50th percentile score means the school grew at the same rate as the national average.
supportive_school_award_desc: This school has not submitted an action plan to support school climate and social & emotional learning (SEL).

healthy_school_certification_1: Students learn better at healthy schools! This school is working towards achieving Healthy CPS. Schools must earn 90% of all criteria to become Healthy CPS. Learn more by visiting  cps.edu/healthycps .
student_attainment_description: Student Attainment measures how well the school performed on standardized tests at a single point in time. This school’s scores are compared to national average scores. A 50th percentile score means the school is performing at the same level as the national average school.
student_growth_description: Student Growth measures the change in standardized test scores between two points in time. This growth is compared to the average national growth for schools that started in the same place. A 50th percentile score means the school grew at the same rate as the national average.
supportive_school_award_desc: This school has not submitted an action plan to support school climate and social & emotional learning (SEL).

student_growth_description: Student Growth measures the change in standardized test scores between two points in time compared other CPS school and schools nationwide. The score is based on an average of the available PSAT and SAT growth measures listed below.

student_attainment_description: Student Attainment measures how well the school performed on standardized tests at a single point in time. This school’s scores are compared to national average scores. A 50th percentile score means the school is performing at the same level as the national average school.
student_growth_description: Student Growth measures the change in standardized test scores between two points in time. This growth is compared to the average national growth for schools that started in the same place. A 50th percentile score means the school grew at the same rate as the national average.
supportive_school_award_desc: This school has put in place systems and structures to support social and emotional learning (SEL). culture_climate_description: Results are based on student and teacher responses to the My Voice, My School 5Essentials survey. For more information on this survey and other measures of school culture and climate visit  https://www.5-essentials.org/ .
healthy_school_certification_1: Students learn better at healthy schools! This school is working towards achieving Healthy CPS. Schools must earn 90% of all criteria to become Healthy CPS. Learn more by visiting  cps.edu/healthycps .
student_attainment_description: Student Attainment measures how well the school performed on standardized tests at a single point in time. This school’s scores are compared to national average scores. A 50th percentile score means the school is performing at the same level as the national average school.
student_growth_description: Student Growth measures the change in standardized test scores between two points in time. This growth is compared to the average national growth for schools that started in the same place. A 50th percentile score means the school grew at the same rate as the national average.
